				h2 Purpose
				p Hotel California exists to propagate environmentally conscious technology, art, and living. We prototype systems, open source the designs, and educate people on how to build and deploy similar systems themselves.
				p We demonstrate our creations at public events throughout the year along with collaborating artists who perform music, massage therapy, body art, comedy, and more.
