				h2 Art & Tech
				p Our biggest projects to date are:
				p 1) A 75 ft long by 25 ft wide mobile arts center. It is assembled without any screws or nails by close fitting joints and tension straps.
				p 2) A 10,000 watt solar power grid which runs a custom music amplifier, speakers and lights––powerful light and sound that is energy-independent.
				p See more on #[a(href="https://www.facebook.com/HotelCaliforniaBM/") Facebook] or #[a(href="https://www.instagram.com/hotelcaliforniabm/") Instagram].
